		"biography":"<table><tr><td><b>HP</b> 184; <b>Bloodied</b> 92<hr><b>Resist</b> half damage from melee and ranged attacks <b>Immune</b> disease, poison, sleep </td><td style=\"padding-left: 15px;\"><b>Init</b> +8 | <b>AP</b> 1 | <b>Save</b> +2</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; background-color:lightgrey; padding:0px 5px 0px 5px;\"><table><tr style=\"border 0px; padding:0px 5px 0px 5px;\"><td><b>AC</b> 29</td><td><b>Fort</b> 25</td><td><b>Ref</b> 26</td><td><b>Will</b> 24</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"padding-left:15px;\"><b>Speed</b> 5, burrow 5 (loose earth only)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; padding:0px 5px 0px 5px;\"><table><tr style=\"border 0px; padding:0px 5px 0px 5px;\"><td>Ability Scores</td><td><b>Str</b> 24 (+13)<br><b>Con</b> 19 (+10)</td><td><b>Dex</b> 15 (+8)<br><b>Int</b> 3 (+2)</td><td><b>Wis</b> 13 (+7)<br><b>Cha</b> 3 (+2)</td></tr></table><td style=\"padding-left:15px;\"><b>Languages</b> -<br><b>Alignment</b> Unaligned</td></tr><tr><td></td><td style=\"padding-left:15px;\"><b>Senses</b> Darkvision<br><b>Passive</b> Perception 17 | Insight 17</td></td></tr></table><hr><table><tr><td><h4><b>Traits</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;⌀ &lt;b&gt;Gusting Sands&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;Aura&lt;/b&gt; 2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Squares within the aura are difficult terrain for enemies. Whenever any enemy attempts to stand up while within the aura, it must make a saving throw. On a failed saving throw, the enemy remains prone and loses the action it used to try to stand.&lt;/p&gt;]] ⌀ <b>Gusting Sands</b> ✦ <b>Aura</b> 2</p><p>Squares within the aura are difficult terrain for enemies. Whenever any enemy attempts to stand up while within the aura, it must make a saving throw. On a failed saving throw, the enemy remains prone and loses the action it used to try to stand.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Unhindered&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;When the golem moves, it pulls with it any creature grabbed by it. In addition, the creature remains grabbed, and the golem does not provoke an opportunity attack from the grabbed creature.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Unhindered</b> <b></b></p><p>When the golem moves, it pulls with it any creature grabbed by it. In addition, the creature remains grabbed, and the golem does not provoke an opportunity attack from the grabbed creature.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Standard</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Slam&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 2 (one creature); +18 vs. AC&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 3d8 + 8 damage, and the golem can grab the target if the golem has fewer than two creatures grabbed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Sustain Free:&lt;/i&gt; The golem sustains each of its grabs.&lt;/p&gt;]] (⚔) <b>Slam</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Attack:</i> Melee 2 (one creature); [[/roll 1d20+18[ vs. AC]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Slam&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 2 (one creature); &lt;u&gt;+18 vs. AC&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 3d8 + 8#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Slam&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 3d8 + 8 damage, and the golem can grab the target if the golem has fewer than two creatures grabbed.&lt;/p&gt;]] <21.5>  damage, and the golem can grab the target if the golem has fewer than two creatures grabbed.</p><p><i>Sustain Free:</i> The golem sustains each of its grabs.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;⚔ &lt;b&gt;Double Attack&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The golem uses slam twice. If both attacks hit, the target or targets of the attacks fall prone.&lt;/p&gt;]] ⚔ <b>Double Attack</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Effect:</i> The golem uses slam twice. If both attacks hit, the target or targets of the attacks fall prone.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Move</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Shifting Sands&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The golem shifts its speed. It ignores difficult terrain and can move through enemies’ spaces during the shift. The golem can instead shift half its speed to also be phasing during the shift. While phasing, it can move through blocking terrain only if that terrain contains a hole or crack that allows air through.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Shifting Sands</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Effect:</i> The golem shifts its speed. It ignores difficult terrain and can move through enemies’ spaces during the shift. The golem can instead shift half its speed to also be phasing during the shift. While phasing, it can move through blocking terrain only if that terrain contains a hole or crack that allows air through.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Minor</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;⚔ &lt;b&gt;Engulf&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will (1/round)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 2 (one creature grabbed by the golem); +14 vs. Fortitude&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 1d10 + 6 damage, and the target takes ongoing 15 damage until the grab ends.&lt;/p&gt;]] ⚔ <b>Engulf</b> ✦ <b>At-Will (1/round)</b></p><p><i>Attack:</i> Melee 2 (one creature grabbed by the golem); [[/roll 1d20+14[ vs. Fortitude]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;⚔ &lt;b&gt;Engulf&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will (1/round)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 2 (one creature grabbed by the golem); &lt;u&gt;+14 vs. Fortitude&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 1d10 + 6#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;⚔ &lt;b&gt;Engulf&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will (1/round)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 1d10 + 6 damage, and the target takes ongoing 15 damage until the grab ends.&lt;/p&gt;]] <11.5>  damage, and the target takes ongoing 15 damage until the grab ends.</p></tr></td></table>",
